Cada vez que terminemos una funcionalidad importante, recuérdame actualizar mi tablero en Notion.\n\n## 5. Política de idiomas en código — comentarios espejo (dual language)\n\nTodo **comentario dentro del código** debe usar el formato **español primero, inglés después**, separados por ` | ` (espacio, barra vertical, espacio).\n\n### Formato\n- **TypeScript / JavaScript:** `// [Español] | [English]`\n- **Python:** `# [Español] | [English]` (misma regla; el símbolo de comentario es `#`).\n- **HTML (plantillas):** `<!-- [Español] | [English] -->` cuando el comentario sea necesario en el markup.\n- **CSS / SCSS:** `/* [Español] | [English] */`\n\n### Ejemplo (TypeScript)\n```typescript\n// Obtener la lista de pedidos desde el servidor | Get the order list from the server\nthis.http.get(url)...\n```"}},{"id":"27dc600c-b07c-4a80-af7b-4ab90ef05b65","values":[-0.0743803083896637,0.00861905887722969,-0.0261002816259861,-0.060830727219581604,-0.09652084112167358,-0.02385796792805195,-0.015603995881974697,0.06960112601518631,-0.007541242055594921,0.04489848017692566,0.008544458076357841,-0.010851165279746056,0.02381259948015213,-0.04288532957434654,0.007545044645667076,-0.023390017449855804,-0.09844530373811722,-0.002934019546955824,-0.027844293043017387,0.004908725619316101,0.08700639754533768,0.0337383970618248,0.01020453404635191,0.07302914559841156,0.0007734685204923153,-0.016331611201167107,-0.025900637730956078,-0.026923615485429764,-0.03839081525802612,-0.0872616395354271,-0.07882402837276459,0.02612048201262951,0.12785540521144867,0.001582297612912953,0.03167319670319557,0.06856732815504074,0.03702836483716965,-0.10164286196231842,-0.026605794206261635,0.019647052511572838,-0.03964589536190033,-0.02678755857050419,-0.027620067819952965,0.03208765760064125,-0.02134835533797741,-0.09038813412189484,-0.017359578981995583,-0.00798613578081131,-0.031107889488339424,0.016225729137659073,-0.04312245920300484,-0.018873853608965874,-0.11231771856546402,0.03099917247891426,-0.0